snippet.title: Beta | Vertical Shift
snippet.description:
Happy Valentines Day!! Because we love you all very much, we have a very special update today. If you head over to our discord , you'll find our latest update Alpha 1.10.25. This is our biggest update ever, featuring a brand new city with people to talk to, places to explore, missions to complete, and a evil corporate government to overthrow. Welcome to Orion! This update will mark the end of our Alpha, next stop will be our Beta launch on SideQuest, App Lab and Itch.io!

Discord: https://discord.gg/xDbK7rs
